@GestionTurnosMedicos.Server_HostAddress = http://localhost:5252

### ========== PACIENTES ==========

### Obtener todos los pacientes
GET {{GestionTurnosMedicos.Server_HostAddress}}/api/pacientes
Accept: application/json

###

### Crear un paciente
POST {{GestionTurnosMedicos.Server_HostAddress}}/api/pacientes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Juan Pérez",
  "cedula": "1234567890",
  "telefono": "555-0123"
}

###

### ========== MEDICOS ==========

### Obtener todos los médicos
GET {{GestionTurnosMedicos.Server_HostAddress}}/api/medicos
Accept: application/json

###

### Crear un médico
POST {{GestionTurnosMedicos.Server_HostAddress}}/api/medicos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Dr. García",
  "especialidad": "Cardiología"
}

###

### ========== TURNOS ==========

### Obtener todos los turnos
GET {{GestionTurnosMedicos.Server_HostAddress}}/api/turnos
Accept: application/json

###

### Crear un turno de prueba
POST {{GestionTurnosMedicos.Server_HostAddress}}/api/turnos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pacienteId": 1,
  "medicoId": 1,
  "fecha": "2026-02-05T00:00:00",
  "hora": "10:00:00",
  "estado": "pendiente"
}

###

### ========== SINCRONIZACIÓN ==========

### Sincronizar SQL a Mongo
POST {{GestionTurnosMedicos.Server_HostAddress}}/api/sync/sql-to-mongo
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Obtener logs de sincronización
GET {{GestionTurnosMedicos.Server_HostAddress}}/api/sync/logs
Accept: application/json

###

### Sincronizar Mongo a SQL
POST {{GestionTurnosMedicos.Server_HostAddress}}/api/sync/mongo-to-sql
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Sincronización bidireccional
POST {{GestionTurnosMedicos.Server_HostAddress}}/api/sync/bidirectional
Content-Type: application/json

